I'd argue about using them forever, Mine is PERMA Banked now (Well its in a bag I got on me).  With the addition of new primary items and forceshield, the epic's appeal has diminished (If you are in a uber guild).<br>
<br>
However not saying you shouldn't try to get your epic, it will server you well if you aren't in the top 10 percent of your server who happen to be in a uber guild.<br>
<br>
Classes that will use their epics forever are:<br>
<br>
1. Cleric - Just to res (Most clerics in my previous guild didn't use it as a primary item)<br>
2. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>BARDS</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Almost every bard I see still wields their epic<br>
<br>
<br>
Thats my list. <br>
<br>
Magicians/Wizards/Enchanters/Necromancers will get a better primary weapon if you are in a uber guild. Example Dagger of thought, Grimoire of Enchantment, Xegony's Wand, Chipped Crystal Staff, etc..<br>
<br>
