<br>
Because it doesn't have the same stacking issues. It stacks with Spiritual Dominion, 9 hp/mana regen per tick, and the Epic doesn't. It also casts in 5 seconds vs 15, something that comes into play during AE fights. I recast FS to suck up the AE damage so I can last longer during the fight and the fact it casts 10 seconds faster means you don't have to wait as long to get back to doing damage. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4380">Qaman</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
